		<item>
		<title>GBPJPY Exchange Rate Has a BoE Rate Meeting Ahead</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/en/analysis/market-news/gbpjpy-exchange-rate-boe-rate-meeting</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 18:39:51 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Market news & Insights]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[GBPJPY]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Recent news]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.atfx.com/?p=33012</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[GBPJPY has rallied ahead of a Bank of England rate meeting.  GBPJPY – Daily Chart  GBPJPY has rallied from support at the 191.50 level and has mounted a three-day rally. The price may meet resistance after the BOJ refuses to accept higher price levels. Necessary support would come in at the 191.50-192 level for the [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">GBPJPY has rallied ahead of a Bank of England rate meeting. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"> <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-33010" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/GBPJPY-–-Daily-Chart.png" alt="GBPJPY – Daily Chart" width="783" height="625" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/GBPJPY-–-Daily-Chart.png 783w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/GBPJPY-–-Daily-Chart-300x239.png 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/GBPJPY-–-Daily-Chart-768x613.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 783px) 100vw, 783px" /></span></p>
